text: Bishnah is a town and a notified area committee in Jammu district in the Indian unon territory of Jammu and Kashmir. This place is located in the Union Territory of Jammu and Kashmir. It is suburban area located in jammu region ==Geography== Bishnah is located at .Falling Rain Genomics, Inc - Bishnah It has an average elevation of 292 metres (961 feet). ==Demographics== India census, Bishna had a population of 9141. Bishna has an average literacy rate of 72%, higher than the national average of 59.5%; with male literacy of 79% and female literacy of 64%. 11% of the population is under 6 years of age. ==Religion== Hindu 97.87%, Sikh 0.46%, Muslim 0.84%.http://www.census2011.co.in ==References== Category:Cities and towns in Jammu district
